@startuml state-auth-session
title Auth Session State Machine

[*] --> Unauthenticated

Unauthenticated --> Authenticating : Login / Register /\nOAuth initiated
Authenticating --> Authenticated : Credentials valid,\ntokens issued
Authenticating --> Unauthenticated : Invalid credentials /\nOAuth cancelled

Authenticated --> TokenExpired : Access token TTL\nexceeded (15 min)
Authenticated --> Unauthenticated : User logs out /\nsession revoked

TokenExpired --> Refreshing : Refresh token\nsubmitted
Refreshing --> Authenticated : Refresh valid,\nnew access token
Refreshing --> SessionExpired : Refresh token\ninvalid or expired

SessionExpired --> Unauthenticated : Redirect to login

@enduml
